	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Vanguard Art Contest - Win a Beta Invite</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Fricka</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Fri, 30 Sep 2005, 14:23:00</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
